	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_UNITED_FRONT_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>The Axis Agreement</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_UNITED_FRONT_HELP">
			<Text>Everywhere, adherents of the true ideology, Autocracy, must put aside their differences and unite. Not until the false religions of Order and Freedom have been extinguished can we rest!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_UNITED_FRONT_HELP_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>Leverage {1_YieldCost} to allow the Foreign Office to yield +5 [ICON_FOOD] Food, [ICON_PRODUCTION] Production, and [ICON_RESEARCH] Science.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_UNITED_FRONT_HELP_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>Give up {1_YieldCost} to gain 3 [ICON_RES_OIL] Oil.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_UNITED_FRONT_HELP_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>Your [ICON_DIPLOMAT] Civil Servants generate -2 [ICON_GOLD] Gold but +2 [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_UNITED_FRONT_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>We need food, schematics and raw materials to continue our war effort. Make what promises we must to our brothers and secure these goods!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_UNITED_FRONT_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>There are organizations out in the world who would do business with us. See that we procure as much Oil as possible from them before our trade routes are cut off!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_UNITED_FRONT_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>We need to put diplomatic pressure on all governments to join our just cause. Put aside what resources we must, this is a fight we must win.</Text>
		</Row>
	</Language_en_US>
